                          I authorise BankBazaar to call/SMS/email me about its products & have accepted the terms of the{' '}
                          <a href="#" className="text-blue-600 underline">Privacy Policy</a>. <button className="text-blue-600 underline">More +</button>
                        </label>
                      </div>

                      <button
                        onClick={() => {
                          setIsSubmitted(true);
